findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function Batchtransfer() uses a loop to transfer for multiple accounts and will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges including changing Uniswap router, modifying fee inclusion/exclusion, updating token amount for swap, modifying marketing address, withdrawing ERC20 tokens, and launching contracts.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to block gas limit.
